## Current Values (from your local setup)

You should have these values from your local .env files:
- DATABASE_URL: Your Neon Postgres connection string
- PINATA credentials: From your Pinata dashboard
- CONTRACT_ADDRESS: 0x127F2a2235141c1838c70B5b91E8a9Cd41d4d7CC
- PRIVATE_KEY: Your wallet private key (keep secret!)

